<bibRefCitation id="EF924B37FFFBFF92FB54F933FED751BD" author="Kurczewski FE &amp; West RC &amp; Waichert C &amp; Kissane KC &amp; Ubick D &amp; Pitts JP" pageId="14" pageNumber="13" pagination="1 - 112" refId="ref25112" refString="Kurczewski FE, West RC, Waichert C, Kissane KC, Ubick D, Pitts JP. 2020 b. New and unusual host records for North American and South American spider wasps (Hymenoptera: Pompilidae). Zootaxa 4891: 1 - 112." type="journal article" year="2020">Kurczewski et al. (2020b)</bibRefCitation>
